{
  "year": 2023,
  "build": "MIXED",
  "description": "RADiCAL in-event head-to-head: 2 DSB1 + 2 LuAG timing capillaries on opposite diagonals (NE/SW = DSB1, NW/SE = LuAG). CERN SPS May 2023. Same DRS4 wiring as DSB1.",
  "_material_map_source": "data-inferred (radcore/inferMixed.C): per-corner timing-cap brightness @150 GeV matched MIXED to pure DSB1/LUAG per corner (SE 526.3~526.4, SW 734.7~734.2, NE 745.5~744.9, NW 411.6~381.1). CONFIRM against logbook.",

  "digitizer": {
    "model": "CAEN DT5742",
    "boards": 2, "groups_per_board": 2, "chans_per_group": 9, "samples": 1024, "sample_ns": 0.2, "hg_sat_mV": 800
